  "description": "<p>在后PC时代传统印刷行业受到了非常大冲击，在改革的阵痛下越来越多的杂志报刊开始走数字化路线。纽约时报就是这样第一批转型的传媒企业，他们试图渐渐抛 弃传统印刷纸质而是转向智能手机和平板等移动终端上。<strong>目前该传媒巨头已经推出了名为“Need to Know”的数字服务，整合了主网站的头条新闻再加上的编辑推荐的有趣新闻，为阅读者打造“便携，信息量丰富”的数字资讯服务。而且该项服务的售价相比较 今年早些时候发布的全数字化应用更加的低廉，每月只需要$15到$35就能就享受这些资讯。</strong></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e980936/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244526.htm&amp;t=%E4%BA%B2%E6%B0%91%E4%BB%B7%E6%A0%BC%2B%E4%B8%B0%E5%AF%8C%E8%B5%84%E8%AE%AF+%E7%BA%BD%E7%BA%A6%E6%97%B6%E6%8A%A5%E6%89%93%E9%80%A0%E2%80%9CNeed+to+Know%E2%80%9D%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244526.htm&amp;t=%E4%BA%B2%E6%B0%91%E4%BB%B7%E6%A0%BC%2B%E4%B8%B0%E5%AF%8C%E8%B5%84%E8%AE%AF+%E7%BA%BD%E7%BA%A6%E6%97%B6%E6%8A%A5%E6%89%93%E9%80%A0%E2%80%9CNeed+to+Know%E2%80%9D%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244526.htm&amp;t=%E4%BA%B2%E6%B0%91%E4%BB%B7%E6%A0%BC%2B%E4%B8%B0%E5%AF%8C%E8%B5%84%E8%AE%AF+%E7%BA%BD%E7%BA%A6%E6%97%B6%E6%8A%A5%E6%89%93%E9%80%A0%E2%80%9CNeed+to+Know%E2%80%9D%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244526.htm&amp;t=%E4%BA%B2%E6%B0%91%E4%BB%B7%E6%A0%BC%2B%E4%B8%B0%E5%AF%8C%E8%B5%84%E8%AE%AF+%E7%BA%BD%E7%BA%A6%E6%97%B6%E6%8A%A5%E6%89%93%E9%80%A0%E2%80%9CNeed+to+Know%E2%80%9D%E6%95%B0